# Rules
1. No bigotry - including racism, sexism, ableism, homophobia, or xenophobia. [Code of Conduct](https://github.com/dessalines/lemmy/blob/master/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md).

1. No Ads / Spamming.

- [Mastodon @LemmyDev](https://mastodon.social/@LemmyDev)
